      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry confirmed by fixture drawings. Material inputs matched to specimen lot data. Rod pre-tension torque (4 Nm) applied identically in simulation and experiment. Equivalency level 3 achieved."
